  RELEVANCE: Shows that epistemic dependence comes in degrees and kinds. Relevant to understanding what is lost when we insist on "figuring it out ourselves" rather than accepting narrative framing from others. Demonstrates that some forms of understanding require accepting others' interpretive work.

